Enum HierarchicalUriComponents.Type

    Enclosing class:
    HierarchicalUriComponents

    static enum HierarchicalUriComponents.Type
extends java.lang.Enum<HierarchicalUriComponents.Type>
    Enumeration used to identify the allowed characters per URI component.

    Contains methods to indicate whether a given character is valid in a specific URI component.

    See Also:
    RFC 3986
